after the movie opens. Not book <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">executives</ENAMEX>. "I'll call an <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">editor</ENAMEX> and ask how a
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">client</ENAMEX>'s book is selling, and he'll say 'Oh, gee, I don't know! Let me check
